{"tid":944772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本15歲乒乓波選手打贏中國23歲選手奪冠","createTime":"2018-12-17T11:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:45:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":519,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3db2295dca4ac3b1062935f23d8d08f57fd323","tid":944772,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/12/17/phpnGsPBv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F17%2FphpnGsPBv.jpg&h=1a355e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">張本智和以15歲之齡在年終賽封王。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕日本球王張本智和昨以15歲6個月之齡，在世界桌球巡迴賽年終總決賽擊敗中國林高遠封王，成為史上最年輕男單冠軍，突破中國此項3連霸壟斷，而長年身為桌壇霸主的中國隊，今年在男女單打、雙打總共只斬獲一座冠軍，反觀日本拿下男單和女雙2座，面對日本新秀來勢洶洶的挑戰，東京奧運也倒數計時，中媒憂心忡忡，「國乒憑什麼應對兩年後的張本智和？」<br />\n<br />\n15歲的張本智和成長快速，一年內相繼擊敗樊振東、張繼科、馬龍、林高遠等中國一線名將，昨天賽後23歲的林高遠承認，輸給年紀小8歲的對手，心態是他最大的問題：「帶著很大的壓力，心態上沒有豁出去，沒有發揮出應有的水平。」<br />\n<br />\n林高遠坦承，相比之下，張本年紀輕輕毫不怯場，在場上很敢拼。張本智和賽後表示，「真的太開心了，真的，在這之前一直想要持續贏過中國的頂尖選手，這是很重要的一勝。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2018/12/17/phpTEqPWf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F17%2FphpTEqPWf.jpg&h=09a8c4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">林高遠（左）坦承，心態上輸給對手是一大關鍵。（歐新社）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，日本另一新星、18歲的伊藤美誠和早田希娜搭檔，昨也在女雙決賽以3：0橫掃中國組合陳幸同／孫穎莎。張本智和和伊藤美誠2人生涯對決中國的勝率都高達5成，下足了工夫，已被中媒列為2年後東京奧運的最大勁敵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2644608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2644608&d=zOsq8nNokY7Vm85B5k8kOE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d4281fd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2644608&h=84c44c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2644608</a>"},{"pid":"918314c97a30e15d601c2151174ffa613c60f629","tid":944772,"uid":94828,"like":487,"dislike":4,"score":483,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"支那仔塊面黑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1b5b4216b16194e39b8417911dabb860726334","tid":944772,"uid":20816,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"恭喜"},{"pid":"809aefb1c6565cbbb44a610ad2f476a3940d0853","tid":944772,"uid":70238,"like":51,"dislike":158,"score":-107,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"其賽呢個日本仔都係支那産品，老豆老母都係歸化日本嘅支那人。"},{"pid":"839cb364b19a3a45c2dd70e2d459877175974221","tid":944772,"uid":126133,"like":388,"dislike":3,"score":385,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"叫睾丸都柒啦，仲要淋嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2205755d9158267570536785082d36e0e3fd41e4","tid":944772,"uid":197563,"like":18,"dislike":11,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"輸心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身就技不如人啦賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbd62f7e6b4c5da58bbb4a9363deb3eb7499da0","tid":944772,"uid":42188,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"支那網民嘅玻璃心又要碎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c9e0a088f4d66b56fe326688de729632a0ee30","tid":944772,"uid":86097,"like":15,"dislike":26,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b95b1b2907981ad30f8abc30989bbaac1f190287","tid":944772,"uid":51701,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"809aefb1c6565cbbb44a610ad2f476a3940d0853","tid":944772,"uid":70238,"like":51,"dislike":158,"score":-107,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"其賽呢個日本仔都係支那産品，老豆老母都係歸化日本嘅支那人。"},"c